title: Uki
resume: Uki is a Belgian animated television series. The main character is a small yellow creature who invites her young viewers to discover the world with her. The show has been airing on Belgian and Finnish networks since April 2010. From September 2011 it was also aired on BBC’s Cbeebies channel, in their Show Me Show Me program.
